<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Bank of China Issues On-line Credit Card </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Different from the traditional credit card, the BOC Intown
Virtual MasterCard contains only a card number, private pin and
electronic certificate for the purpose of online transaction. Card
holders do not have to present the physical card in purchase.
</P>
<P>
Annual fee is waived for the Virtual MasterCard, according to
the BOC, adding that card holders can purchase anything in the
Internet shops that accept MasterCard. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
