<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 17 (Xinhua) -- NCR, a world-leading supplier of
store automation products and solutions, signed a contract today
with Beijing Hualian Hypermarket Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
Under the contract, NCR will supply point-of-sale machines,
servers, and related services to upgrade the operation management
of Beijing Hualian.
</P>
<P>
"This event marks the beginning of a long-term strategic
partnership between NCR and Beijing Hualian. It also demonstrates
the importance NCR attaches to the China market," said Hideki
Hosoi, vice-president of Japan/North Asia Region, NCR's Retail
Solution Group.
</P>
