<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-17 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese Vice-Premier Meets ROK Visitor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Wu Bangguo
met here today with Namgoong Suek, special envoy of the president
of the Republic of Korea (ROK).
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, the two sides exchanged views on furthering
the bilateral cooperation in information and telecommunication
fields.
</P>
<P>
The special envoy conveyed ROK President Kim Dae-jung's wishes
of enhancing the ROK-China cooperation in information and
telecommunication sectors.  
</P>
