the Warehouse 10 to 875 cents, and both Auckland Airport and Sky
TV 4 to 248 and 348 cents respectively.
</P>
<P>
Fletcher Stocks had a good day with Energy up 10 cents to 442
cents, Building 9 to 211 cents, Forests 3 to 54 cents, and Paper 1
cent to 130 cents.
</P>
<P>
AMP fell 26 cents to 1,976 cents, and National Mutual 15 to 290
cents. 
</P>
