Croce said the All-Star guard missed practices a couple of weeks
ago, but the problem was temporarily resolved after a meeting with
Brown.
</P>
<P>
According to general manager Billy King, Iverson phoned the
team trainer Thursday morning to say he had a headache and wouldn'
t participate the 11 a.m. shootaround. King said a headache wasn't
an adequate excuse. 
