civilians, mostly from Linamon, North Lanao, where MILF rebels
mounted a check point after overunning a police detachment.
</P>
<P>
Army soldiers from the 402nd Brigade in North Lanao mounted a
counter offensive killing two MILF combatants, the military said.
</P>
<P>
A battalion of army soldiers from the 402nd brigade in North
Lanao had also been dispatched to regain control of the 80-
kilometerhighways from Linamon to Katapatan, North Lanao.
</P>
<P>
The government forces started to mobilize a massive counter
offensive which included movements of heavy artillery, columns of
tanks and attack helicopters to clear North Lanao highways before
eight o'clock this morning, the military report added.
</P>
<P>
At the moment, all vehicular traffic plying North Lanao, Ozamis,
Pagadian to Zamboanga City were suspended. 
