men's dual moguls title at the Freestyle World Cup finals after
winning the last event of the discipline in Livigno on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Norway's Kari Traa finished third in Thursday's final to beat
Ann Battelle of the United States by 8 points for the women's dual
moguls crown.
</P>
