Trust said the paramedics who went to the terraced house in the
quiet cul-de-sac were "horrified" at what they found.
</P>
<P>
Roads around the Great Hollands estate near Bracknell town
center were sealed off at about 1630 GMT. A police helicopter was
launched to search for the killer. 
